                      "kind": "text",
                      "text": "A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have\na shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or None,\na freshly-allocated array is returned. A tuple (possible only as a\nkeyword argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
                    }
